          blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah.
        </p>
      </div>

      <section class="section about-main">
        <h2>my favorites</h2>
        <div class="enjoy-list">
          <p class="enjoy-row">
            <span class="enjoy-label">GAMES:</span>
            <span class="enjoy-items">Persona 3, VA-11 Hall-A, Fields of Mistria.</span>
          </p>
          <p class="enjoy-row">
            <span class="enjoy-label">BOOKS:</span>
